column2: The way Venezuelans are flocking to bitcoin is astounding. Their inflation is so bad  imagine if you had $100 and could not buy gum.
So  Venezuelans are buying bitcoin in local currency and cash out in stable USD. Foreigners can buy BTC and sell for local prices.
